{"tid":264961,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"（超級難搵）有冇人知咩名","createTime":"2017-05-31T09:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T09:31:24.000Z","uid":46799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e965236d44753d0a605fe33600d8eff4abf9851","tid":264961,"uid":46799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:22:13.000Z","msg":"其實呢套野想搵好耐<br />\n係歐美既一套遇難劇，但係真人真事既，之後再拍出黎，之後每集都會有遇難既真人會講野<br />\n<br />\n係8-9年前明珠台播過，但我有搵過以前既電視播映時間表都冇<br />\n<br />\n內容會有海難咁之類<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知？全能既連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417e3ecba61b9ea3dc75a49f87c185e7fe7e7b7e","tid":264961,"uid":73369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:23:51.000Z","msg":"空襲珍珠海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3ecb1c4c84f8b9253c9e57dd3519df1259e38f","tid":264961,"uid":73369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>空襲珍珠<span style=\"color: red;\">港</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2c84a8288f963824714c6406f1d93233b761f854","tid":264961,"uid":46799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>空襲珍珠<span style=\"color: red;\">港</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係每一集都係唔同事件唔同既遇難，唔係單一事件"},{"pid":"3ac407e63b766ed85ddd7588b3daee13c15f30bf","tid":264961,"uid":46799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2